Class HyperEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Graph.Edge
      • model.Graph.HyperEdge

  • public class HyperEdge
extends Edge
    This is a class for a HyperEdge which extends the class Edge. A HyperEdge is a edge which may have more than one start node/end node and has a label.
